comments: McCollum (POR) moves into Williams (LAC) and delivers body contact that affects Williams' driving shot attempt.
Whiteside (POR) establishes a legal picking position as he firms up in Beverley's (LAC) path. Beverley's reaction isn't consistent with the amount of contact.
As Shamet (LAC) brushes Whiteside's (POR) arm, but the contact is marginal and doesn't affect his natural shooting motion.
Harrell (LAC) establishes a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to Hood (POR).
Hood (POR) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) makes contact to Whiteside's (POR) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Harrell (LAC) establishes himself in McCollum's (POR) path prior to making marginal contact during the pick.
Harrell (LAC) briefly places his hand to Whiteside's (POR) back and immediately disengages by removing his hand.
Shamet (LAC) grabs Simons' (POR) arm and affects his ability to cut to the basket.
Hezonja (POR) legally contests Williams' (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Beverley (LAC) and LIllard (POR) engage and separate off ball.
Whiteside (POR) establishes a legal screening position in Leonard's (LAC) path and absorbs the contact.
Harrell (LAC) legally contests McCollum's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) grabs Whiteside's (POR) left arm and makes contact that affects his ability to rebound. The contact forces him into Beverley (LAC).
Beverley's (LAC) left foot is on the baseline prior to any contact from Lillard (POR).
Harrell (LAC) legally contests Hood's (POR) jump shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) delivers body contact to Leonard (LAC) that affects Leonard's SQBR.
Beverley (LAC) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
Lillard (POR) commits the take foul on Leonard (LAC) prior to any contact from Beverley (LAC).
Leonard (LAC) legally contests Simons' (POR) jump shot attempt.
